		<title>Announcing EY Women in Technology Scholarship for 2021</title>
		<link>https://brainstation.io/blog/ey-women-in-technology-scholarship-renewal</link>
				<pubDate>Thu, 24 Jun 2021 19:30:31 +0000</pubDate>
		<dc:creator><![CDATA[Emily Peck]]></dc:creator>
				<category><![CDATA[BrainStation News]]></category>
		<category><![CDATA[Women in Tech]]></category>
		<category><![CDATA[scholarships]]></category>

		<guid isPermaLink="false">https://brainstation.io/blog/?p=12851</guid>
				<description><![CDATA[<p>BrainStation announces the EY Women in Technology Scholarship will continue this year to make learning opportunities accessible to women around the world.</p>
<p>The post <a rel="nofollow" href="https://brainstation.io/blog/ey-women-in-technology-scholarship-renewal">Announcing EY Women in Technology Scholarship for 2021</a> appeared first on <a rel="nofollow" href="https://brainstation.io/blog">BrainStation® Blog</a>.</p>
]]></description>
								<content:encoded><![CDATA[
<p>We are excited to announce that the&nbsp;<a href="https://brainstation.io/scholarships?utm_source=newsletter&amp;utm_medium=email&amp;utm_campaign=EYScholarshipJune22"><em>EY Women in Technology</em>&nbsp;<em>Scholarship</em></a><em>&nbsp;</em>will continue for another year.&nbsp;</p>



<p>Since 2012, we have awarded more than $2 million in scholarship funding, empowering over 100,000 professionals around the world with digital skills training. Over the last 12 months, Ernst &amp; Young LLP (EY) has been a steadfast supporter in this mission, helping to promote diversity and inclusion in the workplace and to make learning opportunities accessible to as many women as possible around the world.</p>



<p>Like BrainStation, EY recognizes the importance of closing the global gender and skills gap, and working together, we will continue to have a positive impact on gender disparity – in the tech industry and beyond.&nbsp;</p>



<figure class="wp-block-image size-large"><a href="https://brainstation.io/scholarships?utm_source=newsletter&amp;utm_medium=email&amp;utm_campaign=EYScholarshipJune22"><img src="https://d1jxdyr49kipv5.cloudfront.net/prod/wp-content/uploads/2021/06/24150452/Quote-Card-EY-Mockup-1024x512.jpg" alt="Quote from Catherine Hunter, Partner, Technology Transformation at EY Canada" class="wp-image-12852" srcset="https://d1jxdyr49kipv5.cloudfront.net/prod/wp-content/uploads/2021/06/24150452/Quote-Card-EY-Mockup-1024x512.jpg 1024w, https://d1jxdyr49kipv5.cloudfront.net/prod/wp-content/uploads/2021/06/24150452/Quote-Card-EY-Mockup-300x150.jpg 300w, https://d1jxdyr49kipv5.cloudfront.net/prod/wp-content/uploads/2021/06/24150452/Quote-Card-EY-Mockup-768x384.jpg 768w, https://d1jxdyr49kipv5.cloudfront.net/prod/wp-content/uploads/2021/06/24150452/Quote-Card-EY-Mockup-1536x768.jpg 1536w, https://d1jxdyr49kipv5.cloudfront.net/prod/wp-content/uploads/2021/06/24150452/Quote-Card-EY-Mockup-2048x1024.jpg 2048w, https://d1jxdyr49kipv5.cloudfront.net/prod/wp-content/uploads/2021/06/24150452/Quote-Card-EY-Mockup-960x480.jpg 960w, https://d1jxdyr49kipv5.cloudfront.net/prod/wp-content/uploads/2021/06/24150452/Quote-Card-EY-Mockup.jpg 2400w" sizes="(max-width: 1024px) 100vw, 1024px" /></a></figure>



<p>“EY is very proud to continue working with BrainStation to increase access to digital skills education. We remain committed to promoting diversity and closing the gender pay gap in our workplaces, and by improving digital literacy, we can knock down significant barriers for women at all levels,&#8221; said Catherine Hunter, Partner, Technology Transformation at EY Canada.</p>



<p>The&nbsp;<a href="https://brainstation.io/scholarships?utm_source=newsletter&amp;utm_medium=email&amp;utm_campaign=EYScholarshipJune22"><em>EY Women in Technology</em>&nbsp;<em>Scholarship</em></a> reduces barriers for the many talented, ambitious women looking to pursue a digital career.&nbsp;</p>



<p>All women looking to develop skills in any of the following digital fields are eligible:&nbsp;</p>



<ul><li>Data</li><li>Design</li><li>Development</li><li>Marketing</li><li>Product&nbsp;</li><li>Business</li></ul>



<p><a href="https://brainstation.io/book-call?utm_source=newsletter&amp;utm_medium=email&amp;utm_campaign=EYScholarshipJune22">Please speak to a Learning Advisor</a>&nbsp;to find out more about the&nbsp;<em>EY Women in Technology Scholarship</em>.</p>
<p>The post <a rel="nofollow" href="https://brainstation.io/blog/ey-women-in-technology-scholarship-renewal">Announcing EY Women in Technology Scholarship for 2021</a> appeared first on <a rel="nofollow" href="https://brainstation.io/blog">BrainStation® Blog</a>.</p>
]]></content:encoded>
